com.attivio.sdk.client.trigger

Class TriggerDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.attivio.sdk.client.trigger.TriggerDefinition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable

    public class TriggerDefinition
extends Object
implements Cloneable, Serializable
    Defines a trigger, which is used for matching documents during ingestion processing.

    A trigger is uniquely identified in a dictionary by its name.
